    "description_long": "This is a large, two-story suburban house with a brick exterior and a complex, multi-gabled roof. The property is surrounded by a fence and features a spacious driveway with a circular turnaround, as well as a gated entrance. The backyard includes a rectangular swimming pool, a paved patio area, and is bordered by rows of trees for privacy. The front facade is symmetrical, with a prominent central entryway flanked by windows and shrubbery. The house is set within a landscaped yard, with greenery and trees lining both the front and rear perimeters.",
